<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178663>
    bibo:endPage "68" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "61" ;
    bibo:volume "1595" ;
    dc:creator "Botero-Trujillo, Ricardo" ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Ananteris Thorell (Scorpiones: Buthidae) from Colombia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178665>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178666>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178664> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178665>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 7. Ananteris myriamae sp. nov., female holotype (MPUJ-SCO- 245). 3. Right chelicera, dorsal view; 4. Coxosternal region, genital operculum and pectines; 5. Sternites I – III showing median hyaline and smooth areas, and booklung spiracles; 6. Anterior margin of the carapace; 7. Metasomal segments IV – V and telson, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178665/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178666>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 13. Distribution of the trichobothria in female holotype Ananteris myriamae sp. nov. (MPUJ-SCO- 245). 8. Right femur, dorsal and external views; 9. Left femur, internal view; 10. Right patella, dorsal view; 11. Right patella, external view; 12. Right chela, external view; 13. Left chela, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178666/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178664>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Known distribution of Colombian Ananteris." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178664/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

